Kell Brook will fight Frankie Gavin on May 30 at the O2 in London . 
  Brook beat Jo Jo Dan for the IBF World Welterweight title in Sheffield last month . 
  The welterweight will return to action on a pay-per-view show in May . 
  Brook will face Gavin rather than bitter rival Amir Khan . 
